query: SELECT COUNT(*) as total, SUM(CASE WHEN dataCompetencia IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as nullComp, SUM(CASE WHEN dataCompetencia = '' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as emptyComp, SUM(CASE WHEN dataEmissao IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as nullEmis FROM notas n JOIN clientes c ON c.id = n.clienteId WHERE c.razaoSocial LIKE '%ALLBATROZ%';
